trans-unit.source:
Kamaelia is a library of components you can take and bolt together, and
customise. This includes components for TCP/multicast clients and servers,
backplanes, chassis, Dirac video encoding &amp; decoding, Vorbis decoding, pygame &amp;
Tk based user interfaces and Tk, visualisation tools, presentation tools, DVB
(freeview) games tools, a visual system builder, open gl &amp; bit torrent&hellip;
